        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(ui): improve Workboard task details",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- make Workboard cards compact by moving expanded metadata, proof, diagnostics, worker logs, automation, protocol state, events, and operator notes into a detail drawer\n- keep execution safe from the drawer: active/linked/archived cards do not expose duplicate start paths, stale task cache is ignored when session lifecycle is authoritative, and recent proof/events stay visible\n- clarify the dispatcher tool copy and fix owner capacity so unclaimed review cards free a slot while claimed review cards still block duplicate starts\n- sync generated Control UI locale fallbacks for the new Workboard strings\n\n## Verification\n\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.ui.config.ts --configLoader runner ui/src/ui/controllers/workboard.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/workboard.test.ts` (75 tests)\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run extensions/workboard/src/dispatcher.test.ts` (4 tests)\n- `node --import tsx scripts/control-ui-i18n.ts check` via local pnpm/oxfmt shim (clean, fallback-only locales)\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main` (clean: no accepted/actionable findings)\n\n## Remote proof notes\n\n- Testbox `tbx_01kt0hjqyeej16ek2d2dgwpq9b` ran `pnpm check:changed` and reached typecheck; it failed on an unrelated `extensions/phone-control/index.test.ts` fixture issue from latest main, which was then fixed upstream and dropped from this branch during rebase.\n- Later Testbox attempts (`tbx_01kt0jfr0k20d21csaty9b0as1`, `tbx_01kt0jpsp2f9jj2h77cb0x1jk2`) failed before executing tests due Blacksmith SSH/rsync sync/auth failures.\n- Azure fallback full check `run_829e7ca90f28` used the wrong sparse-worktree lane and failed on missing sparse-excluded `security/opengrep/check-rule-metadata.mjs`; Azure sparse-safe retry `run_8f71051b980b` waited ~11 minutes for capacity and was stopped before lease allocation.\n",
